Description: 此配置文件应拷贝到程序的配置目录里，作为VGT的缺省显示组件
Text: entityTypes中,Entity指除了中心天体CentralBody之外的其它对象类型，如Satellite,Facility等
LastUpdate: 20240619, 修改了Angle、Plane里笔误的问题，属性值无法获取，提示内显示为undifined

Point.name: Center
tips: 说明:对象的质心点

Point.name: L1
tips: 说明:Central bodies aligned axes of selected libration point between one primary and multiple secondary central bodies with with X-axis along position of libration point relative to primary center of mass and Z-axis along orbit normal of libration point relative to primary center of mass.

Point.name: L2
tips: 说明:Central bodies aligned axes of selected libration point between one primary and multiple secondary central bodies with with X-axis along position of libration point relative to primary center of mass and Z-axis along orbit normal of libration point relative to primary center of mass.

Point.name: L3

tips: 说明:Central bodies aligned axes of selected libration point between one primary and multiple secondary central bodies with with X-axis along position of libration point relative to primary center of mass and Z-axis along orbit normal of libration point relative to primary center of mass.

Vector.name: East

说明:垂直于自身椭球体表面法向量的单位向量,且指向当地水平面内东方向

说明:垂直于自身椭球体表面法向量的单位向量,且指向当地水平面内北方向

System.name: L2
tips: 类型说明:坐标系由原点和参考轴组成
说明:L2 libration point system aligned with Libration axes and centered on L2 point.

Angle.name: SunMoon
tips: 类型说明:两个向量的夹角
说明:视太阳向量和视月球向量的夹角

Angle.name: VelocityAzimuth
tips: 类型说明:二面角:两个向量绕第2个轴向量形成的夹角
说明:当地北方向与惯性系速度方向的夹角(绕位置矢量)

Angle.name: VelocityAzimuth
tips: 类型说明:二面角:两个向量绕极轴向量形成的夹角
说明:当地水平面内，北方向与固定系速度方向的夹角(向东为正)

Angle.name: SunAzimuth
tips: 类型说明:二面角:两个向量绕极轴向量形成的夹角
说明:当地水平面内，北方向与视太阳方向的夹角(向东为正)

Angle.name: SunZenithDistance
tips: 类型说明:两个向量的夹角
说明:当地天顶方向和视太阳向量的夹角

Angle.name: VertFlightPath
tips: 类型说明:两个向量的夹角
说明:垂直飞行路径角,惯性系下位置和速度的夹角

Angle.name: Beta_Sun
tips: 说明:视太阳向量与轨道面的夹角

Angle.name: Beta_Moon
tips: 说明:视月球向量与轨道面的夹角

Plane.name: LocalHorizontal
tips: 类型说明:参考坐标系的6个平面之一
说明:对象自身椭球体当地水平面,X轴指向当地北,Y轴指向当地东

Plane.name: Trajectory
tips: 类型说明:对象相对参考系的瞬时位置、速度组成的平面
说明:对象在中心天体惯性系下的轨道平面,X轴指向位置矢量方向,Y轴约束在惯性系速度方向
